        text: "Shri Sant Gajanan Maharaj College of Engineering, Shegaon, is committed to fostering an inclusive and equitable campus environment that upholds the dignity of all individuals irrespective of gender. The institution has constituted a Women Development Cell, Prevention of Sexual Harassment Committee, and Anti-Ragging Committee to ensure a safe and supportive atmosphere."
